nals, fostering a collaborative and high-performance work environment.\n\nOversee & negotiate contracts with vendors, service providers, and third-party partners to ensure favourable terms and service quality.\n\nEnsure compliance with regulatory requirements and manage risks associated with hotel operations & asset management.\n\nPrepare and present performance reports to stakeholders, highlighting achievements, challenges, and strategic initiatives.\n\nImplement and monitor programs to enhance guest satisfaction and address issues proactively.\n\nPlan and oversee renovation and improvement projects, ensuring they are completed on time, within budget, and to quality standards.\n\nDrive continuous improvement initiatives and adopt new tech and practices to enhance operational efficiency and guest experience.\n\nDevelop and implement contingency plans to address unforeseen challenges and ensure business continuity.", "experiences/0/jobLocation": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/0/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "2-2024", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D0BAQETd2Af29JcQA/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1665126890204?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=J85LfWmaGe4REIUXI-e3lW5StUtYRBmu_5Vnk3Wi0Cw", "experiences/0/title": "General Manager", "experiences/1/companyId": "18850341", "experiences/1/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/1/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/boulevard-hotel-bangkok/", "experiences/1/companyName": "Boulevard Hotel Bangkok", "experiences/1/companySize": "51-200", "experiences/1/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:18850341", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "(Operated & Managed by Resolute Hotels & Resorts)\nSupporting and Directing Operations, whilst ensuring quality and consistency in service. ensuring guests have an outstanding stay, and remember how the warmth of our hospitality makes