est experience.\n\n• Work closely with F&B Director to create incentives with rooms division to encourage direct bookings and joint F&B promotions. \n\n• Coordinate with all departments to ensure the cost per occupied room is within the budget. Ensure the operations team are aware and actively coached on methods to upsell and extend stay to reduce commission per occupied room.\n\n• Lead by example and liaise with guests in house to ensure guest feedback is within KPI target.\n\n• Listen to all staff ideas and implement processes that they feel will assist their operations.\n\n• Work with the sales team to guide and motivate them to achieve desired short-stay and long-stay corporate business.\n\n• Analyse P&L to ensure the hotel is achieving financial targets.\n\n• Implement Quality Assurance measures throughout the hotel, Including perfect room set-up and targetted guest feedback scores.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "1-2024", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/2/jobLocationCountry": "SG", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "2-2023", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQErPO6l6gbnvA/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1630563792519/oakwood_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=EN_j-LzrTuhImWI-TLSSGGS6EHOZzLejL0nx21SFKx8", "experiences/2/title": "Hotel Manager", "experiences/3/companyId": "14376671", "experiences/3/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/3/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/siamatsiamdesignhotelpattaya/", "experiences/3/companyName": "Siam@Siam Design Hotel Pattaya", "experiences/3/companySize": "201-500", "experiences/3/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:14376671", "experiences/3/companyWebsite": "http://www.siamatpattaya.com", "experiences/3/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/3/jobDescription": "Support, empower, motivate, and lead key HODs in managing front-of-house and back-of-house operations. We work together to follow the 