ital.\n\n- Managing online guest messaging account. Dealing with ASQ guest issues. Liaising with all guests pre-arrival, in house, and upon departure. The main point of communication for all pre-arrival guest enquiries.\n\n- Created and analysed post-ASQ stay survey to provide ongoing improvements to guest in-house experience regarding guest journey comfort and safety.\n\n- Conducted regular health and safety meetings with the Thai government, under ASQ safety guidelines provided by The ministry of public health and the ministry of defense.\n\n- Liaising with sales & reservations in promoting ASQ packages and driving avenues of guest feedback to correct online platforms to increase sales of ASQ packages. Designed VIP ASQ stay packages.\n\n- Supporting the F&B department to ensure guest dietary requirements are followed and communicated efficiently. Conducting quality control standards of ASQ operations.\n\n- Planned and presented financial P&L report to GM for ASQ Operating budget. Planned and budgeted P&L VIP group bookings sales for sports teams requiring ASQ accommodation.\n\n- Supporting Engineer departments and renovation of room set up per requirements set by The Ministry of public health for ASQ operations.\n\n- Facilitated accurate joint hotel operations for ASQ medical tasks. Supporting housekeeping in hygiene and in-room setup.\n\n- Conducted regular meetings with all HODs regarding ongoing operations for the ASQ project.", "experiences/5/jobEndedOn": "3-2022", "experiences/5/jobLocation": "Bangkok Metropolitan Area", "experiences/5/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/5/jobStartedOn": "8-2020", "experiences/5/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/5/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4D0BAQEH-qEa5vSwEQ/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1631340821127?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=grkdMEayI3Uzhb48QY4DhMh5i1GKB-IQ3qrMGMZimOI", "experiences/5/title": "Crisis Operations Project Manager", "experiences/6/companyId": "13630287", "experiences/6/co