iderably in my role during our time working together.", "recommendations/1/name": "Kunihiro (Kuni) K.", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Experienced Hospitality Leader", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kuniluther/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJC9CsBUQou6k0QS-ox-qVWYJxlpMTHmQI", "recommendations/2/context": "Luis Fernando was senior to Clive but didn't manage Clive directly", "recommendations/2/date": "October 31, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "Luis is an expert in his field of Sales & Marketing.\nHe has extensive knowledge of all segments relating to rooms' top-line production and is exceptional at developing relationships with travel agents, as well as analysing the latest tourism trends to adjust the approach to various market mix to maximise revenue targets.\nHe possesses an outgoing nature and coaches members of his team to work on their own initiative.\nDuring our time working together at Rembrandt Hotel, it was a pleasure running operations under Luis' guidance from the Sales department, which he led with confidence and in a personable and friendly manner.", "recommendations/2/name": "Luis Fernando Arjonilla Muñoz", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Passionate Executive Hotel Sales & Distribution Leader/ Strategic Market Planner/ Hybrid supplier & buyer expert/ Team Cohesion booster/ Hotel Tech enthusiast/ Sales Record Breaker/ APAC & EMEA professional/ Data lover", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/luis-fernando-arjonilla-muñoz-21a1881b/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQeezYB6f3Psov9bjOuChQ2xpanPiASL-4", "recommendations/3/date": "February 28, 2022", "recommendations/3/description": "Moustafa has superb initiative and incredible motivation in achieving his targets. This admirable trait also encourages everyone to achieve more in the work and studies. Moustafa exhibits exceptional leadership skills, which was a great assistance in our marketing module for the MBA we studied together. His knowledge of medical supplies and how these are marketed gave useful insight in this industry and exceptionally highlighted his authentic leadership style by empowering myself and our colleagues to meet our goals together.", "recommendations/3/name": "Moustafa SALAH, MBA", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Franchise Lead Cardio Metabolic at Servier Middle East | Marketing | Certified Digital Marketing", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/moustafa-salah-mba-4b40498/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFuA4gBpD6dd667QpEfgilBMJUiFFWwsBs", "recommendations/4/context": "Clive was senior to Fabien but didn't manage Fabien directly", "recommendations/4/date": "May 7, 2020", "recommendations/4/description": "Fabien takes immense pride in creating a restaurant outlet, which focuses on the perfect dining experience, as well as exquisite food. Both myself and Fabien worked together to develop his restaurant team in enhancing their service mind capabilities. His knowledge and passion for hospitality made it a pleasure to work with him!", "recommendations/4/name": "Fabien B.", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Directeur d'ESMSS | Gérontologie | Sociologie et Vieillissement | Expert Thématique au Laboratoire des Solutions de Demain (CNSA)", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/fabienboissonade/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB9BB9UBd3m0bs-w7hHuCpmGBwoSwYrI8kI", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Clive was Cees 'KC''s client", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "November 4, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Clive is an amicable hotelier pur sang. Friendly personality and extremely suitable for his (new-) role at Siam @ Siam Design Hotel in Pattaya. An amazing venue with amazing facilities. I've hosted a couple of fairly large functions at this trendy hotel and good memories travel with me since then...", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Cees 'KC' Cuijpers", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Serial Entrepreneur", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kcpattaya/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHHHEYBLA_eQbRZfGYZEYTcGbcRnldLiSA", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Sascha was Clive's client", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "November 2, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Clive is a hands-on and very personable Hotel Manager, with a keen eye for detail, and goes out of his way to ensure guests receive a perfect stay.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Sascha Kunze", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Cluster GM Hotel Muse Bangkok, Autograph Collection & Metropole, Bangkok, a Tribute Portfolio", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sascha-kunze-7261b124/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUDEc4BROTmIZaFtwj_tU37-VnKvph78xc", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Kunihiro (Kuni) was senior to Clive but didn't manage Clive directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "November 2, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I had a pleasure working with Clive at 137 Pillars Suites and Residence Bangkok. He's such an energetic gentleman who can be flexible, easy to work with and adaptable in any work environment.   Trustworthy and heartfelt approach to any staffs.  He's a great asset.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Kunihiro (Kuni) K.", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Experienced Hospitality Leader", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kuniluther/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABJC9CsBUQou6k0QS-ox-qVWYJxlpMTHmQI", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Jacques worked with Clive on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "November 2, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Mr Clive, always display a positive attitude and was highly supportive of all management initiatives, especially training department and operations. He has always demonstrated, honesty, integrity, and professionalism. I have no hesitation recommended Clive to any future employer as I am confident that he will continue to prove himself a valuable asset to any organization. I wish him all the best.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Jacques Varet", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "General Manager FCC Angkor by Avani", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jacques-varet-38392173/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA-extMBFEjPN1BnOG9HkmA7y_sNwjzF7xk", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "November 1, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "During my MBA program, I had the pleasure of meeting Clive in a study group. Clive really aided our study group's exam preparation by sharing insights from his own professional expertise. I can tell with certainty that Clive is a quick learner, dedicated to finishing the tasks he is involved in, but most importantly, he is a true team player. Any organization that Clive is a member of would definitely benefit from his capacity to seek answers and his professional work ethic.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Michelle Taylor", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Chief Information Officer | MBA|CISM|DPO", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michelle-taylor-65745b83/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABGvwuMB7SKw4ng3Z2lQEy_L3p5GMyKH3gQ", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Dmitry worked with Clive on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "November 1, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Clive is a quick learner and very adaptive to a new working environment. He is expertise in hotel  operation, guest experiences as well as possess with extensive knowledge in commercial side of hotel business. Good team leader and always set samples for others to follow. ", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Dmitry C.", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "General Manager Movenpick | MBA Burapha University", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dmitry-c-0701a124/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUCvRQBX_Ne7qnZ4uaWebDRo9mwn0gKGeo", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Luis Fernando was senior to Clive but didn't manage Clive directly", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "October 31, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "I have worked with Clive in Rembrandt for over 3 years and I cannot stress enough his hands on attitude and amazing ability to learn at a micro and macro environmental scope. Over the course of this time his resilience, problem solving ability, optimal operational upkeeping, customer care excellence and key shareholder relationship competences really shined. I would certainly recommend any cooperation with Clive as a business partner or within the hotel management structure as a key performer on all scopes as a reliable and efficient professional.\nIt was a pleasure to work together during our time at Rembrandt.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Luis Fernando Arjonilla Muñoz", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Passionate Executive Hotel Sales & Distribution Leader/ Strategic Market Planner/ Hybrid supplier & buyer expert/ Team Cohesion booster/ Hotel Tech enthusiast/ Sales Record Breaker/ APAC & EMEA professional/ Data lover", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/luis-fernando-arjonilla-muñoz-21a1881b/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQeezYB6f3Psov9bjOuChQ2xpanPiASL-4", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Fabien worked with Clive on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "May 7, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I had the pleasure and the privilege to work with Clive on developing staff at Rembrandt Hotel in Bangkok. \nClive is a very benevolent and creative professional in terms of Quality management as well as a very efficient pedagogue\n. ", "recommendationsR