ortable. What truly set her apart, however, was her remarkable talent for handling guest complaints and challenging situations with professionalism, confidence, and care.\n\nShe had a rare ability to find solutions that satisfied both the guest and the hotel - something that is far easier said than done in hospitality. Kathleen understood when empathy and patience were needed, but she was equally capable of taking a firm and professional stance when dealing with unreasonable or difficult situations.\n\nShe was dependable, highly capable, and someone you could always trust to represent the resort to the highest standard. Beyond her skills, Kathleen also contributed greatly to the atmosphere of the workplace. Her presence made the resort a better place for both guests and staff alike.\n\nI would have no hesitation in recommending Kathleen to any future employer. She would be a valuable addition to any hospitality team.", "recommendations/0/name": "kathleen Dirangga", "recommendations/0/subtitle": ".", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kathleen-dirangga-4baa83175/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACmgpw4BNpQ7adsDU6eRYNqZXeG9jAfJpU0", "recommendations/1/context": "Ciaran was senior to Júlia but didn't manage Júlia directly", "recommendations/1/date": "August 30, 2013", "recommendations/1/description": "Julia is a very detailed oriented person who strives to deliver high customer service to guests. Her passion for the job shines through on a daily basis and she was a pleasure to work with. \n\nHer ability to solve guests issues was second to none and it was a pleasure having here at the resort. \n\nThe team at Sensimar Khaolak wishes her all the best in her future endeavors and hope that our paths will cross again in the future.", "recommendations/1/name": "Júlia Neto", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Senior Program Director", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/julianeto/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profi